------

+ Attention all site directors,
In an effort to create a more stable backup system and contingency plans, I have begun work on Project [DATA EXPUNGED]. However, one hold up that I would like to request assistance for involves the relocation of spacial or geographic anomalies. 

Site-814 and SCP-[DATA EXPUNGED] are being constructed for the purpose of harboring anomalies that defy are understanding of physical space, and if we could develop a method of moving large areas of land, we could potentially re-classify dozens of SCPs to the Safe designation.
[[/div]]
